W. H. Graeser, alias W. H. Grazer, Plaintiff in Error, v. State of Florida, Defendant in Error. A writ of Error to a. Judgment of the Criminal Court of Record within and for the County of Duval. F. D. Brennan, for Plaintiff in Error;

Writ of Error dismissed on motion of counsel for plaintiff in error.

No appearance for Defendant in Error.
